            <section id='western'>
                <article>Western Astrology</article>
                <dl>
                    <dt>Aries</dt>
                    <dd>           Aries is energetic, straight forward, and brave. They are good at initializing activities 
                        with an intensity, and any mistakes they make with poor planning can easily be made up with yet more 
                        dynamism.</dd>
                    <dt>Taurus</dt>
                    <dd>            Taureans are reliable, stubborn, and connoisseur's of pleasure from all senses. 
                        Capabale of storing much energy, they are ready to endure patiently until prospects reach fruition. </dd>
                    <dt>Gemini</dt>
                    <dd>            Gemini is the definitive human sign, representing all aspects of the human condition most accurately. 
                        Endowed with the ability of expression and lightning fast wit, this jack of all trades mercurial tendencies 
                        can excel in a variety of departments. </dd>
                    <dt>Cancer</dt>
                    <dd>            Cancer is an intuitive and creative sign that values security in home, finances, and emotions. They can 
                        seem crusty on the outside, until you gain the trust of this intelligent and funny leader. </dd>
                    <dt>Leo</dt>
                    <dd>            Leo is a sign of pride, ego and self-expression. Creative, likeable, and generous, this dominant individual 
                        harness' the power of the sun to illuminate their surroundings. </dd>
                    <dt>Virgo</dt>
                    <dd>            Virgos are intelligent, detail oriented and methodical. Their realistic view on reality can lead to 
                        pessimism, due to the inevitability of their perfectionism going unsatisfied.</dd>
                    <dt>Libra</dt>
                    <dd>            Libras are a sign of harmony, social grace, and partnership. Ruled by Venus, they are naturally artistic, and 
                        as an air sign they are communicative. They like to be the best, and impress people with their 
                        outlandish antics. Being that Libra's are the newest sign, they can also be frivolous, deceptive, 
                        duplicitious, and sadistic. </dd>
                    <dt>Scorpio</dt>
                    <dd>            Scorpios are a sign of intensity, passion, and emotions. They get deeply involved in love and relationships, 
                        and are prone to revenge if irrevocably slighted. Like a scorpion in your shoe, they can exist under the 
                        radar until the opportune moment when you will no longer ignore their presence and power. </dd>
                    <dt>Sagittarius</dt>
                    <dd>            Sagittarians are somewhat of a jovial clownish philosopher. They have an open-minded and no strings 
                        attached philosophy, seeking to understand and travel the world. Being the archer, they are straight 
                        shooters, and can suffer from foot in mouth syndrome with their blunt language. </dd>
                    <dt>Capricorn</dt>
                    <dd>            Capricorn implies you are a hardworking individual that epitomizes the zenith of  
                        aspiration. The leader of signs, well rounded and ambitious, shows much prowess in all endeavors. </dd>
                    <dt>Aquarius</dt>
                    <dd>                Aquarians are natural innovators, and not only do they walk to the beat of a different drummer, they 
                        probably crafted the drum itself. Humanitarian, intellectual, and communicative, they have great 
                        ability to connect with people. </dd>
                    <dt>Pisces</dt>
                    <dd>                Pisces are comprised of all the the qualities of the zodiac. Mystical, inuitive, psychic, creative, 
                        Pisces see's into the spritual realm. The two fish swimming in opposite directions represent the 
                        humans power of choice, the master of one's own fate, for better or worse. </dd>
                </dl>
