                <dl>
                    <dt>Rat</dt>
                    <dd>The rat is intelligent, sociable, and energetic.</dd>
                    <dt>Ox</dt>
                    <dd>Oxes are known for being hardworking, strong, dependable, and honest. </dd>
                    <dt>Tiger</dt>
                    <dd>Tigers are known as brave, competitive, and thrill seeking. </dd>
                    <dt>Rabbit</dt>
                    <dd>Rabbits are known as intelligent, elegant, sensitive, and appreciative of the finer things in life. </dd>
                    <dt>Dragon</dt>
                    <dd>Dragons are powerful, assertive, enthusiastic, egotistical, and doesn't take criticism well. </dd>
                    <dt>Snake</dt>
                    <dd>Snakes are wise, good at speaking, suceeding in life, and overly sexual.</dd>
                    <dt>Horse</dt>
                    <dd>Horse's are energetic, very apt with skills, hardworking, sociable, and like to perform. </dd>
                    <dt>Goat</dt>
                    <dd>Goats are naturally artistic, creative, stylish, and reserved. While they don't like to be the center of 
                        attention, they like to be recognized for their unique skills. </dd>
                    <dt>Monkey</dt>
                    <dd>Monkey's are witty, intelligent, curious and versatile. They like practical jokes and breaking the rules, and not 
                        everyone responds to their relentless ruse.</dd>
                    <dt>Rooster</dt>
                    <dd>Roosters are active, sociable, honest, and artistic. They like being attractive, loyal, and expressing their opinions. </dd>
                    <dt>Dog</dt>
                    <dd>        
                        Dogs are loyal, nice, sociable, somewhat cautious and anxious. They like to perform for others, 
                        and are well liked by peers. </dd>
                    <dt>Pig</dt>
                    <dd>        Pigs are hardworking, generous, and nice. They concentrate on their tasks well, and thrive at their 
                        ambitions. Though bubbly and humorous on the outside, they have a dark side as well. </dd>
                  </dl>
